                Voulez-vous vraiment appliquer ces modifications maintenant ?
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="modal-footer border-0 pt-0 pb-4 px-4 justify-content-end gap-2">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary px-4 fw-500" id="btn-cancel-confirm-task">
                Annuler
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger px-4 fw-500" id="btn-force-task-save">
                <i class="bi bi-check-lg me-2"></i> Confirmer
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
